flowPara.tspan: When you act despite an imminent threat, say how you deal with it and flip.
✷ by powering through or enduring, flip
✷ by getting out of the way or acting fast, flip
✷ with quick wits or via mental fortitude, flip
On a ✅ / ✔✔, the GM may ask you a question, offer you a worse outcome, hard bargain, or ugly choice
Make progress, but stumble, hesitate, flinch
You do it, but there's a new complication
